{"type":"article_comment","id":359194,"parentType":"article","parentId":18189,"uid":9304,"contents":"渥太华学员纪念四二五 加议员赞誉法轮功<br>\n<br>\n4月24日中午，<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E6%B8%A5%E5%A4%AA%E5%8D%8E?src=hashtag_click\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#渥太华</a> 几位法轮功学员代表当地学员，前往中加使馆前纪念四二五和平上访21周年，呼吁停止对 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E6%B3%95%E8%BD%AE%E5%8A%9F?src=hashtag_click\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#法轮功</a> 学员的迫害。<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7?src=hashtag_click\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#加拿大</a> 自由党国会议员思格若赞扬说，法轮功学员坚定不移地维护道义和信仰，并谴责仍在发生的迫害。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/card_img/1254183423062704128/CKr3bWjQ?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/card_img/1254183423062704128/CKr3bWjQ?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/card_img/1254183423062704128/CKr3bWjQ?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\nhttps://www.epochtimes.com/gb/20/4/25/n12060632.htm","date":"2020-04-25","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}